{{~##
Bar Chart Partial - Lumina Statistics Extension

Reusable bar chart component for statistics data.
Used by overview.revela for all chart sections.

Expects variables set before include:
- chart_title: Chart heading text
- chart_items: Array of { name, count, percentage }
##~}}
<h3>{{ chart_title }}</h3>
<dl>
{{~ for item in chart_items ~}}
    <dt data-count="{{ item.count }}">{{ item.name }}</dt>
    <dd style="--percent: {{ item.percentage }}"></dd>
{{~ end ~}}
</dl>
